Friendliness.LowDescription: You are a private person and don't let many people in
Friendliness.HighDescription: You make friends easily and feel comfortable around other people

Gregariousness.LowDescription: You have a strong desire to have time to yourself
Gregariousness.HighDescription: You enjoy being in the company of others

Assertiveness.LowDescription: You prefer to listen than to talk, especially in group situations
Assertiveness.HighDescription: You tend to speak up and take charge of situations, and you are comfortable leading groups

Activity-level.LowDescription: You appreciate a relaxed pace in life
Activity-level.HighDescription: You enjoy a fast-paced, busy schedule with many activities

Excitement-seeking.LowDescription: You prefer activities that are quiet, calm, and safe
Excitement-seeking.HighDescription: You are excited by taking risks and feel bored without lots of action going on

Cheerfulness.LowDescription: You are generally serious and do not joke much
Cheerfulness.HighDescription: You are a joyful person and share that joy with the world

Trust.LowDescription: You are wary of other people's intentions and do not trust easily
Trust.HighDescription: You believe the best in others and trust people easily

Cooperation.LowDescription: You do not shy away from contradicting others
Cooperation.HighDescription: You are easy to please and try to avoid confrontation

Altruism.LowDescription: You are more concerned with taking care of yourself than taking time for others
Altruism.HighDescription: You feel fulfilled when helping others, and will go out of your way to do so

Morality.LowDescription: You are comfortable using every trick in the book to get what you want
Morality.HighDescription: You think it is wrong to take advantage of others to get ahead

Modesty.LowDescription: You hold yourself in high regard, satisfied with who you are
Modesty.HighDescription: You are uncomfortable being the center of attention

Sympathy.LowDescription: You think that people should generally rely more on themselves than on other people
Sympathy.HighDescription: You feel what others feel and are compassionate towards them

Self-efficacy.LowDescription: You frequently doubt your ability to achieve your goals
Self-efficacy.HighDescription: You feel you have the ability to succeed in the tasks you set out to do

Orderliness.LowDescription: You do not make a lot of time for organization in your daily life
Orderliness.HighDescription: You feel a strong need for structure in your life

Dutifulness.LowDescription: You do what you want, disregarding rules and obligations
Dutifulness.HighDescription: You take rules and obligations seriously, even when they're inconvenient

Achievement-striving.LowDescription: You are content with your level of accomplishment and do not feel the need to set ambitious goals
Achievement-striving.HighDescription: You have high goals for yourself and work hard to achieve them

Self-discipline.LowDescription: You have a hard time sticking with difficult tasks for a long period of time
Self-discipline.HighDescription: You can tackle and stick with tough tasks

Cautiousness.LowDescription: You would rather take action immediately than spend time deliberating making a decision
Cautiousness.HighDescription: You carefully think through decisions before making them

Anxiety.LowDescription: You tend to feel calm and self-assured
Anxiety.HighDescription: You tend to worry about things that might happen

Anger.LowDescription: It takes a lot to get you angry
Anger.HighDescription: You have a fiery temper, especially when things do not go your way

Depression.LowDescription: You are generally comfortable with yourself as you are
Depression.HighDescription: You think quite often about the things you are unhappy about

Self-consciousness.LowDescription: You are hard to embarrass and are self-confident most of the time
Self-consciousness.HighDescription: You are sensitive about what others might be thinking about you

Immoderation.LowDescription: You have control over your desires, which are not particularly intense
Immoderation.HighDescription: You feel your desires strongly and are easily tempted by them

Vulnerability.LowDescription: You handle unexpected events calmly and effectively
Vulnerability.HighDescription: You are easily overwhelmed in stressful situations

Artistic-interests.LowDescription: You are less concerned with artistic or creative activities than most people who participated in our surveys
Artistic-interests.HighDescription: You enjoy beauty and seek out creative experiences

Emotionality.LowDescription: You do not frequently think about or openly express your emotions
Emotionality.HighDescription: You are aware of your feelings and how to express them

Adventurousness.LowDescription: You enjoy familiar routines and prefer not to deviate from them
Adventurousness.HighDescription: You are eager to experience new things

Intellect.LowDescription: You prefer dealing with the world as it is, rarely considering abstract ideas
Intellect.HighDescription: You are open to and intrigued by new ideas and love to explore them

Liberalism.LowDescription: You prefer following with tradition in order to maintain a sense of stability
Liberalism.HighDescription: You prefer to challenge authority and traditional values to help bring about positive changes
